            "id": 6011725,
            "title": "何立峰將訪英 舉行中美經貿磋商機制首次會議",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中國外交部發言人周六（7 日）晚間宣布，應英國政府邀請，中共中央政治局委員、中國國務院副總理何立峰將於 6 月 8 日至 13 日訪問英國，其間將與美方舉行中美經貿磋商機制首次會議。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011725%2Fl%2Ff48d775ddb2b8e3907d26ea6c0cc9ad7.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">何立峰將訪英，舉行中美經貿磋商機制首次會議。（圖：Shutterstock）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國總統川普周五已經在社群平台 Truth Social 上宣布，財政部長貝森特、商務部長盧特尼克、美國貿易代表葛里爾將於下周一（9 日） 在倫敦與中國代表舉行會談，討論貿易協議相關事宜。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據《央視》報導，中國國家主席習近平周四晚應約同川普通話，兩國元首同意雙方團隊繼續落實日內瓦共識，儘快舉行新一輪會談。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><br/>\n </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
